  "texts": [
    "Users may quickly grasp the document's substance without having to read the whole thing thanks to the global summary, which gives them a clear and thorough overview of the entire document.",
    "This summarizing tool is very helpful for students who need to quickly process a lot of information.",
    "By applying a Large Language Model (LLM) to uploaded text, the flashcard generating tool creates study aids that support active recall and spaced repetition learning approaches.",
    "When a user uploads instructional materials to the system, this process starts.",
    "After obtaining the content, the LLM examines the writing to pinpoint crucial terms, definitions, and pertinent information."
